    "body": "This issue seems to be an issue on M1 macs.\r\n\r\nOn the M1, hardhat tries to download the wasm build by looking at this json:\r\nhttps://binaries.soliditylang.org/wasm/list.json\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, for some reason there is no wasm build of solidity for 0.5.17\r\n\r\nThis issue seems to be being tracked in the solidity project here:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/10329\r\n\r\nI eventually managed to get 0.5.17 working. I'm not sure if it was installing rosetta, downgrading to node 14, or some other thing I tried.\r\n\r\n0.5.16 according to the changelog is pretty much the same so you could use that version for now.\r\n",
